11:
Everywhere they go, there will be things that cause them to be terrified;
\q2 it will be as though those things were pursuing them and biting at their heels.
\q1

13:
Diseases will spread all over their skin;
\q2 diseases will cause their bodies to decay.
\q1

17:
No one on the earth will remember them anymore;
\q2 no one on any street will even remember their names.
\q1
